org.itsnat.core.event

Interface ItsNatEventDOMStateless

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.w3c.dom.events.Event, ItsNatDOMExtEvent, ItsNatEvent, ItsNatEventStateless, ItsNatNormalEvent, ItsNatUserData

    public interface ItsNatEventDOMStateless
extends ItsNatEventStateless, ItsNatDOMExtEvent
    This event type is the case of event stateless when dispatched to a global document listener because a document template was specified in request.

    Default implementation inherits from java.util.EventObject.

    Author:
    Jose Maria Arranz Santamaria
